extends layout

block content
	include navbar
	include breadcrumb

	main
		section#content.section--content
			.container
				.mb-4.mb-xl-5
					+breadcrumb([{name: 'Home', url: 'index.html'}, {name: 'Restgo'}])
				.text-center.mb-4.mb-xl-5
					h1.display-4.fw-bold.mb-3 Restgo
					p.h4.fw-bold.mb-4 Booking a pool villa
					div
						| Conducted user research and designed a pool villa booking system, including search, booking flow, and responsive cross-platform components.

				.mockup-image.p-4.p-xl-5
					img(src="../assets/images/mockup/com/DUO-5.png").img-single

				.row.g-3.g-md-4.mb-5
					.col-12.col-md-6
						.card.h-100.bg-light.border-0
							.card-body
								.h5.fw-bold 
									i.far.fa-file-alt.me-2.text-secondary
									| Overview
								.card-text Restgo is an online platform that allows users to search and book private villas and vacation homes in Thailand. The main objective of this project is to improve the user experience by simplifying the accommodation search process and making the booking journey more intuitive.
					.col-12.col-md-6
						.card.h-100.bg-light.border-0
							.card-body
								.h5.fw-bold 
									i.far.fa-times-circle.me-2.text-secondary
									| Problem
								.card-text Users who are planning group trips or vacations often struggle to quickly find suitable villas that match their needs, such as location, capacity, and amenities. If the browsing and booking process is not clear, users may abandon the website before completing a reservation.
								hr(style="opacity: .15;")
								.h6.fw-bold Pain Points
								.card-text.mb-1 - Difficult to quickly compare villas
								.card-text.mb-1 - Users need to open many pages to see details
								.card-text - Booking process may require multiple steps
					.col-12.col-md-6
						.card.h-100.bg-light.border-0
							.card-body
								.h5.fw-bold 
									i.fas.fa-bullseye.me-2.text-secondary
									| Goal
								.card-text The goal of this design is to help users find and book villas faster by simplifying the search experience and highlighting key information.
								hr(style="opacity: .15;")
								.h6.fw-bold UX Goals
								.card-text.mb-1 - Improve villa discovery
								.card-text.mb-1 - Simplify the booking process
								.card-text - Help users compare accommodation options quickly
					.col-12.col-md-6
						.card.h-100.bg-light.border-0
							.card-body
								.h5.fw-bold 
									i.fas.fa-pencil-ruler.me-2.text-secondary
									| Design Solution
								.card-text To improve usability, the interface highlights search functionality and presents villa listings in a clear card layout. Key information such as price, location, and capacity is displayed prominently so users can quickly compare accommodation options.
								hr(style="opacity: .15;")
								.h6.fw-bold UX Improvements
								.card-text.mb-1 - Improved search visibility
								.card-text.mb-1 - Clear villa card design
								.card-text - Simplified booking flow
					.col-12
						.card.h-100.bg-light.border-0
							.card-body
								.h5.fw-bold 
									i.fas.fa-tachometer-alt.me-2.text-secondary
									| Result / Impact
								.card-text The improved interface helps users find suitable villas more efficiently and complete bookings with fewer steps, resulting in a smoother and more intuitive user experience.

				.mockup-image-list.mb-4.mb-xl-5
					img(src="../assets/images/restgo/mobile-restgo-07.png").w-mobile
					img(src="../assets/images/restgo/mobile-restgo-03.png").w-mobile
					img(src="../assets/images/restgo/mobile-restgo-01.png").w-mobile

				.mockup-image-list--desktop.mb-4.mb-xl-5
					.row.g-3.g-md-4.align-items-center
						.col-12.col-md-6
							img(src="../assets/images/restgo/desktop-restgo-01.png")
						.col-12.col-md-6
							img(src="../assets/images/restgo/desktop-restgo-05.png").mb-3.mb-md-4
							img(src="../assets/images/restgo/desktop-restgo-02.png")

				.mockup-image-list--desktop.mb-4.mb-xl-5.bg-transparent
					.row.g-3.g-md-4
						.col-4
							img(src="../assets/images/restgo/017.png").w-sm
						.col-4
							img(src="../assets/images/restgo/sceen-restgo-04.png").w-sm
						.col-4
							img(src="../assets/images/restgo/sceen-restgo-05.png").w-sm

				.mockup-image-list--desktop.mb-4.mb-xl-5(style='height: 800px;')
					.row.g-3.g-md-4.justify-content-center
						.col-6.col-md-4
							img(src="../assets/images/restgo/sceen-restgo-02.png").w-sm
						.col-6.col-md-4
							img(src="../assets/images/restgo/sceen-restgo-03.png").w-sm

	include footer
